  Game information:
  =================

  Prepare to beat the records and compete in 10 intoxicating  Winter  sports. 
  Become the Winter champion and take part in exciting contests on  the  most 
  thrilling ice surfaces and snow pistes in the world. Immerse yourself in  a 
  fantastic competition atmosphere and be right up close as a  Winter  sports 
  athlete when victory in a competition means a hundredth of a second!
 
  Prove yourself in  the  enthralling  Single  Player  mode,  or  compete  in 
  riveting multiplayer matches in split screen mode on one console. Take your 
  team to the icy top of the  Winter  sports  world  in  over  a  variety  of 
  breathtaking challenges and emotionally charged competitions!
